How about splitting this method into two:
ContentPreviewer requestContentPreviewer(ctx, RequestHeaders headers);
ContentPreviewer responseContentPreviewer(ctx, RequestHeaders reqHeaders, ResponseHeaders resHeaders);
I guess the behavior of response previewer might be affected by a certain request header, e.g. x-enable-content-preview: 1.

